tected H_2D^+ and D_2H^+ lines towards the core\nI16293E, and the H_2D^+ line observed towards Oph D can be reproduced using the\npresent excitation model and the physical models suggested in the original\npapers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Nov 2009 12:13:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Jan 2010 07:55:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
